# ===================================================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING:
# ===================================================================
# If maps don't show:
# 1. Check that all API keys are present
# 2. Verify APIs are enabled in Google Cloud Console
# 3. Check Android SHA-1 fingerprint is added (for MAPS key)
# 4. Rebuild the app: npx expo prebuild --clean
# 5. Create development build: npx expo run:android
# 6. Check logs: npx expo start --dev-client
#
# If directions fail:
# 1. Ensure Directions API is enabled
# 2. Check that DIRECTIONS key has correct APIs enabled
# 3. Monitor requests in Google Cloud Console > APIs & Services > Metrics
# 4. Look for 4xx errors indicating permission issues
#
# If places search fails:
# 1. Ensure Places API and Places API (New) are enabled
# 2. For mobile, PLACES key restrictions should be "None" or "HTTP referrers"
# 3. Check that you're not hitting quota limits
# ===================================================================